Your invocation looks wrong (think: `func` is pointer to function):

Replace this line:

    (objects[i].func)();

*with* 

    (objects[i].*func)();

That being said, I would highly recommend using `std::function` and perhaps also `std::bind` instead of &#39;*raw function pointers*&#39; (when it looks like you are not constrained by a 3rd party library).

